		<description><![CDATA[Talk like a pirate? A more impressive challenge: Walk like a pirate Sail the ocean blue No GPS as a guide Just sun, moon and stars Starving for fresh fruit Scurvy fatigues, rots the gums Spoiled meager stores Raiding by surprise Cruelty, debauchery The pox inflames below On second thought, no Keelhaul that whole idea [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop --><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><div class='shareaholic-like-buttonset' style='float:right;height:30px;'><a class='shareaholic-fblike' data-shr_layout='button_count' data-shr_showfaces='false' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesecretlair.com%2Fmain%2F2011%2F09%2F22%2Fhaiku-theatre-talk-like-a-pirate-day-edition%2F' data-shr_title='Haiku+theatre%3A+Talk+Like+A+Pirate+Day+edition'></a><a class='shareaholic-googleplusone' data-shr_size='medium' data-shr_count='true' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesecretlair.com%2Fmain%2F2011%2F09%2F22%2Fhaiku-theatre-talk-like-a-pirate-day-edition%2F' data-shr_title='Haiku+theatre%3A+Talk+Like+A+Pirate+Day+edition'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop --><p><div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 650px"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/leshoward/236800781/"><img title="CC BY-NC image from leshoward via Flickr" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/96/236800781_7f7af453ac_z.jpg?zz=1" alt="CC BY-NC image from leshoward via Flickr" width="640" height="354" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">CC BY-NC image from leshoward via Flickr</p></div></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Talk like a pirate?<br />
A more impressive challenge:<br />
Walk like a pirate</p>
<p><div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 650px"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/gadgetgirl70/1427451365/"><img title="CC BY-NC-ND image from gadgetgirl via Flickr" src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1167/1427451365_994b08d05a_z.jpg" alt="CC BY-NC-ND image from gadgetgirl via Flickr" width="640" height="427" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">CC BY-NC-ND image from gadgetgirl via Flickr</p></div></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Sail the ocean blue<br />
No GPS as a guide<br />
Just sun, moon and stars</p>
<p><div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 650px"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/celebdu/59954109/"><img alt="CC BY image from celebdu via Flickr" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/26/59954109_2369d9dc8a_z.jpg" title="CC BY image from celebdu via Flickr" width="640" height="480" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">CC BY image from celebdu via Flickr</p></div></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Starving for fresh fruit<br />
Scurvy fatigues, rots the gums<br />
Spoiled meager stores</p>
<p><div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 490px"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/kindle/4745886910/"><img alt="CC BY-NC-ND image from twelves via Flickr" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4114/4745886910_e1e7b6c72f_z.jpg" title="CC BY-NC-ND image from twelves via Flickr" width="480" height="640" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">CC BY-NC-ND image from twelves via Flickr</p></div></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Raiding by surprise<br />
Cruelty, debauchery<br />
The pox inflames below</p>
<p><div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 650px"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/28122162@N04/4965444930/"><img alt="CC BY-ND image from vladeb via Flickr" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4128/4965444930_690548092e_z.jpg" title="CC BY-ND image from vladeb via Flickr" width="640" height="512" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">CC BY-ND image from vladeb via Flickr</p></div></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">On second thought, no<br />
Keelhaul that whole idea<br />
I&#8217;ll stick with &#8220;Aye, Yar!&#8221;</p>
<p><div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 430px"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/lilcrabbygal/1442227286/"><img alt="CC BY-NC-ND image from Vanessa Pike-Russell via Flickr" src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1176/1442227286_9efec943d2_z.jpg" title="CC BY-NC-ND image from Vanessa Pike-Russell via Flickr" width="420" height="640" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">CC BY-NC-ND image from Vanessa Pike-Russell via Flickr</p></div></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8230;..</p>
<p><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/us/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4190" title="CC BY-NC-SA" src="http://www.thesecretlair.com/main/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/80x15.png" alt="CC BY-NC-SA" width="80" height="15" /></a><br />
<h3><em><br />
The above haiku collection is a part of a series of short fiction by John Cmar inspired by randomly discovered Creative Commons licensed images, and is itself licensed under a <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/us/">Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial-Share Alike 3.0 United States License</a>.</em></h3>
